{
  "stem": "8786.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is in 1940.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I forgot to mention before that in 1938, November the 2nd-- this just occurred to me-- Hitler and the Hungarian government, they became close friends.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the Hungarians on their own, they were anti-Semites on their own style, not what they became later.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyway, because of this friendship, Hungary was given back a part of Slovakia, and that included my town too.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just to-- for the record, in 1919, Hungary lost the war, the First World War, and it was chopped up a little bit.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The northern part, the eastern part became to Romania.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The northern part was a part became a new entity, which is called Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the south, Yugoslavia was created.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And on the north in [INAUDIBLE], even Austria was given a piece.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So because of Hitler was the boss, became the boss of Europe, and they had a-- they call it the Viennese Conference, Ciano and-- Daladier, I don't know whether he was there-- but Hitler and Mussolini and his friends chopped up Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Slovakia became a-- a puppet government.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the southern part of Slovakia, which was occupied by many Hungarian people, was given back to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now all of a sudden we became back Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And Hungary was-- as I said before, was already busy with their anti-Jewish laws.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They did it on their own, but they wanted to please Hitler, because Hitler was-- he wanted to 100%.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were just going step by step.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "First it was the first Jewish law.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Sure enough, when I became about 13 years old, all of a sudden the Hungarian government asked every Jewish businessman to send in their licenses.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
